  "id": "5c4ad8c828e76300171ae403",
  "title": "概念とメタファー",
  "created": 1548409036,
  "updated": 1548471284,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c4ad8c828e76300171ae403",
      "text": "概念とメタファー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409036,
      "updated": 1548409036
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ad8cbaff09e0000d502c5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a038c898a7d3f8440c262fb3165a9b05]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409036,
      "updated": 1548409303
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ad9d7aff09e0000ee2a69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409303,
      "updated": 1548409303
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ad9e9aff09e0000d502c6",
      "text": "[概念]と[メタファー]の関係について",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409321,
      "updated": 1548409338
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ad9faaff09e0000d502c7",
      "text": "\t抽象概念の理解を支えているのがメタファー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409338,
      "updated": 1548409357
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ada0daff09e0000d502c9",
      "text": "\t\t[メタファーによる理解]は、[アナロジー]、[類推]、[連想]などを基本とする認知",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409357,
      "updated": 1548409408
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ada41aff09e0000d502ca",
      "text": "\t\tメタファーはしばしば、[個人的経験]と強く紐づいている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409409,
      "updated": 1548409425
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ada51aff09e0000d502cb",
      "text": "\t\t同じ[経験]をした人同士では、[たとえ話]がスムーズに伝わりやすい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409426,
      "updated": 1548409450
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ada6baff09e0000d502cc",
      "text": "\t\t言語を介さずに[経験を共有]することでスムーズな[情報伝達]の土台を作ろうというのが[共同化]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409451,
      "updated": 1548409502
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4ada07aff09e0000d502c8",
      "text": "\t支えられている抽象概念",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409351,
      "updated": 1548471280
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4bcbefaff09e000057101c",
      "text": "\t\t概念を習得した人同士でスムーズな情報伝達をするための[制度化した言葉]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548471280,
      "updated": 1548471284
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4adbbeaff09e0000ff6665",
      "text": "\t\t[数学]の議論などに特徴的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409790,
      "updated": 1548471269
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4adc72aff09e0000ff6668",
      "text": "\t\t\t[論理]や用語の[定義]など、いくつかのことを「正しい」とする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409970,
      "updated": 1548409997
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4adc8caff09e0000ff6669",
      "text": "\t\t\tこの「正しさ」に合意をした人の間の情報伝達手段",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409997,
      "updated": 1548410008
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4adc47aff09e0000ff6667",
      "text": "\t\t\t人によって判断が異ならないようにするために意図的に個人的経験への依存性が取り払われている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409927,
      "updated": 1548410010
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4adc41aff09e0000ff6666",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548409921,
      "updated": 1548409921
    }
  ]
}